    {
      "id": "6RYZEfZ3xIRRBbl9E5C9o",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3372.472028878672,
      "y": 1074.9812347529507,
      "width": 776.2394409179688,
      "height": 725,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b65",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 965920952,
      "version": 996,
      "versionNonce": 1855229384,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779788561057,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Ultimate Goal: \nClick a button, and generate a custom schedule for the day with my context\nand prefrences.\n\nWhat is my context?\n- Todos\n- Things I want to achieve (missions)\n- Repeating events/tasks\n- Prayer times\n\nWhat is my prefrences?\n- Freetime control (so I don't fall)\n- Working around prayer times\n- Not working so much, but not too little\n- Including my hobbies in the day\n\nIf the agents knows these things will they generate a good schedule?\nI guess so\n\nBut what if I want to add more context/things the agent should think about?\nex: \n- صله الرحم\netc..\n\nDo I add another sub agent under the time related agent?\nor\nDo I add more context to the time related agent?\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Ultimate Goal: \nClick a button, and generate a custom schedule for the day with my context\nand prefrences.\n\nWhat is my context?\n- Todos\n- Things I want to achieve (missions)\n- Repeating events/tasks\n- Prayer times\n\nWhat is my prefrences?\n- Freetime control (so I don't fall)\n- Working around prayer times\n- Not working so much, but not too little\n- Including my hobbies in the day\n\nIf the agents knows these things will they generate a good schedule?\nI guess so\n\nBut what if I want to add more context/things the agent should think about?\nex: \n- صله الرحم\netc..\n\nDo I add another sub agent under the time related agent?\nor\nDo I add more context to the time related agent?\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
